Minecraft Myth Busting Playlist ► https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL7VmhWGNRxKi1ikLc2b_pi6EIGOCdF10d
In this first "Mini Myths" episode we take a look at 5 different myths, cobwebs & fall damage, mobs on water & ice, beacons with redstone and other blocks, fortune iii on glowstone and nether star's explosion resistance.
